title: #92Noon! Vox In The Box: Dean Evason, Michael Russo, Matt Majka, Ryan Carter, Tom Reid
description: The undefeated Vox In The Box is back! Wild Interim Head Coach Dean Evason joins the show at the start, Michael Russo talks the road ahead, Former Wild and White Bear Lake Bear Ryan Carter brings his perspective about the Wild to the box, Wild President Matt Majka stops by to talk about his role for the team, and Tom Reid discusses his future games working with PA!
